title: A MASTERPIECE COLLECTION (Compilation CD)
description:
A MASTERPIECE COLLECTION [Classical Compilation CD]________________________________
 

155 PIECES - NEARLY 13 HOURS OF MUSIC, AND ITS ALL HERE ON ONE 700MB CD COMPILATION

Please do not bitch about the tags, bitrates, or otherwise - They are good quality. I've spent enough time putting this disc together and normalizing the volume throughout. Most should ring familiar with everyone. These are -most- of the very popular classical pieces out there. I know that there are more that should be here and some may think that a few should not. This covers a wide range - from standard familiar pieces to movies, themes, cartoons (you'd be surprised), commercials, holidays, and more... ENJOY

- - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - -
